thread.title: Tieto will cooperate in digitalisation of cancer diagnosis in Västergötland
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Tieto will cooperate in digitalisation of cancer diagnosis in Västergötland | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Tieto will cooperate in digitalisation of cancer diagnosis in Västergötland
text:
Sept 24 Tieto Oyj :
* Will cooperate in digitalisation of cancer diagnosis in Västergötland
* Agreement is valid for 10 years, value is 46 million euros ($51.6 million)
* Extension option for another 10 years Source text: bit.ly/1iNthMs
 ($1 = 0.8917 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
